title: King Arthur’s Excalibur Letter Opener with Stand, Office Accessory, Home Decor, Gift for Collectors, Fans

UNIQUE & FUNCTIONAL: Our Sword is an alternative decorative item for your house as well as it is a unique functional item for your office. It is produced with attention to create detailed symbol that is engraved beautifully on the blade, quillon, and pommel.

PERFECT GIFT: Fans of Merlin, King Arthur, or those who are interested in this legendary sword will be crazy for our Excalibur Letter Opener.
